{"type": "article", "id": 15064, "title": "网状材质，不对称或层叠的裙摆｜每天都有流行关键词", "description": "我们每天为你总结秀场流行元素。", "date": "2015-09-17T15:06:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 16206, "name": "渔网"}, {"id": 10698, "name": "露肩"}, {"id": 16207, "name": "黑白灰"}, {"id": 16208, "name": "不对称"}, {"id": 16209, "name": "裙摆"}, {"id": 16210, "name": "层叠"}, {"id": 2837, "name": "DKNY"}, {"id": 16211, "name": "Milly"}, {"id": 16212, "name": "Marchesa"}, {"id": 16173, "name": "Boss"}, {"id": 1653, "name": "Michael Kors"}, {"id": 2911, "name": "Anna Sui"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605195710nKLIt3pSv4adONZY.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t不对称裙摆：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\t不对称的元素在秀场上总是很常见，从肩部的剪裁到腰部的镂空，左右不同的袖子，这一季不对称的裙摆也多次出现。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605195704aqt9BQcr6vG1ySMI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t美国很火的新锐品牌 Proenza Schouler （上图），由两位年轻设计师创立（下图），旗下最受欢迎的当属 PS1 包，是不少好莱坞明星的心头好。他们此次带来的作品仍然有很多露肩设计（几乎所有品牌这一季都超爱，也许接下来可以开个“露肩特辑”）、网状材料和羽毛、蝴蝶结<span>……</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060519570559vRDJEQ0Fhr78fG.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.22407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t改朝换代的 DKNY，找来 Public School 的设计师组合 Dao-Yi Chow 和 Maxwell Osborne 任创意总监，还换了新的 Logo。这一季 DKNY 的秀场基本由黑白灰三色统治，不少中性的美式休闲打扮。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605195705Tu5kDa7icANhfUml.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>DKNY </em><span style=\"text-align:center;\">△</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em></em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605195706Dp3X7F9ymTSQGo08.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span></em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Milly</em>△\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605195706APsphTRXrmG3laM8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Narciso Rodrigue</em> <span style=\"text-align:center;\">△</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t网状材料：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t渔网袜随处可见，不再有那么多的禁忌，想穿就穿。不少品牌也默契地使用了很多网状材料和镂空设计，比如上面提到的 <span> Proenza Schouler ：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605195707Atj5VCYcxh1PqSzW.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606051957077YbnZvt0wPp1Cras.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span><em>Proenza Schouler </em></span>△\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606051957082GqBReQX1jD3y5oN.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Anna Sui</em> △\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606051957086tvdxTV3e5lLaSDn.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>Marchesa </em>△\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t层叠裙子设计：\r\n</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t虽然这种层层叠叠多了，也许可以叫“蛋糕裙”，除了模特可能没人穿得好看，但秀场上确实出现不少。少叠几次好看些？\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605195709ZjiRpefB8DWxOwFC.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tMichael Kors Collection <span style=\"text-align:center;\">△</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605195709BzcZEIrAm1QeiqDv.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tProenza Schouler △\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605195710g2TKcjUml4SGrCL8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75407925\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tDKNY <span style=\"text-align:left;\">△</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}